import { ThemeProvider, BaseStyles, Box } from '@primer/react'
import { Navigation } from './components/Navigation/Navigation'
import { SelectHeader } from './components/SelectHeader/SelectHeader'

function App() {
    return (
        <ThemeProvider colorMode="light">
            <BaseStyles>
                <Navigation />
                <Box>
                    <SelectHeader />
                </Box>
            </BaseStyles>
        </ThemeProvider>
    )
}

export default App
